What Is Birla Sun Life Insurance ?
Birla Sun Life Insurance Company Limited -LRB- BSLI -RRB- is a joint venture between Aditya Birla Group of India and Sun Life Financial Inc of Canada . Birla Sun Life Insurance Company provides life insurance products to the residents of India . The life insurance sold by this company is not sold in the US .
Birla Sun Life Insurance Company is a joint venture between the Aditya Birla Group and Sun Life Financial , Inc. . It is a very large life insurance company in India.The AUM of Birla Sun Life Insurance is close to Rs 22,929 crs and it has a capital base of over Rs . 2,450 crs as on Mar 31 , 2013 . Sun Life Financial is a highly rated company , as is the Aditya Birla Financial Services Group -LRB- ABFSG -RRB- .
