What Is Postal Life Insurance Bonus Rate ?
I know that postal workers have group life insurance , but the one thing many postal workers over look is there life insurance can increase over 300 % through out your career and after retirement start to decrease when i ` ts needed the most . What i recommend is do a review of your life insurance policy , because any bonus that you may want or think is available really wont matter if your life insurance decreases every year in retirement .
